WEBVTT

00:09.080 --> 00:11.160
The Sikong family's realm

00:12.600 --> 00:15.040
Cannot be stained with the blood of our own clan again

00:34.440 --> 00:35.960
Father clearly said this wound was almost healed

00:36.720 --> 00:37.280
How is this

00:38.280 --> 00:39.640
I've thought for a long time

00:41.440 --> 00:44.200
And decided to pass the throne to your elder brother

00:49.080 --> 00:50.640
In times of chaos

00:51.880 --> 00:54.240
Xuan Kingdom needs bravery

00:54.560 --> 00:56.840
Fierceness and ruthlessness

01:03.640 --> 01:05.400
But to govern in peace

01:05.840 --> 01:07.200
Your elder brother is more suitable than I

01:07.840 --> 01:08.720
Or you

01:08.720 --> 01:10.000
More suitable

01:16.800 --> 01:19.360
Do you think I'm being unfair?

01:21.480 --> 01:22.080
No

01:22.920 --> 01:25.480
Your son is willing to assist elder brother

01:30.400 --> 01:31.920
I remember everything

01:32.640 --> 01:34.480
The Tiannan Pass battlefield

01:34.960 --> 01:37.680
You alone lured Shilang into the pass

01:38.240 --> 01:39.160
That battle

01:41.600 --> 01:43.160
You were hit by two blades

01:43.960 --> 01:45.440
Got back on your horse and fought again

01:46.880 --> 01:47.640
Further north

01:49.240 --> 01:50.440
Your chest

01:51.520 --> 01:52.400
Shoulder

01:53.040 --> 01:53.880
Back

01:55.800 --> 01:57.000
All have arrow wounds

01:58.360 --> 02:00.880
Every wound you suffered for Xuan Kingdom

02:02.480 --> 02:03.680
I remember

02:06.760 --> 02:07.400
Father

02:12.600 --> 02:14.440
Your temper is most like mine

02:15.520 --> 02:17.040
I sometimes think

02:17.720 --> 02:19.200
When the realm is at peace

02:20.320 --> 02:23.200
You can travel the mountains and rivers for me

02:24.160 --> 02:27.280
See beautiful scenery and people everywhere

02:28.280 --> 02:29.640
Free as an immortal

02:33.520 --> 02:35.080
But after all, some things

02:36.400 --> 02:38.640
I must burden you with

02:39.680 --> 02:40.240
Father

02:45.360 --> 02:47.560
Your elder brother has it hard

02:48.080 --> 02:49.440
Help him for me

02:50.760 --> 02:51.760
Assist him

02:53.760 --> 02:55.640
And protect what we two

02:55.960 --> 02:58.560
Worked so hard to conquer

03:00.560 --> 03:01.440
Second son

03:04.080 --> 03:05.440
Can you promise me?

03:11.240 --> 03:12.400
Your son promises

03:13.320 --> 03:18.160
Your son guarantees to do everything to protect Xuan Kingdom

03:21.160 --> 03:22.320
Rise

03:29.320 --> 03:30.840
Good child
